data.text: @raidenzerox PCO is the IT guy of 2018. Someone who was on nobody's radar this time last year. A number of in demand acts were unknown rookies just 2 years ago. The fact that so many indy workers & promotions are doing good & making money should kill that boogeyman myth.

@raidenzerox The indies will be crippled when people stop financially supporting them. The talent pool never dries up contrary to popular internet belief. New people always rising up & old faves returning along with forgotten or unknown folks making waves.

@5Deuce4Tre7 Fans don't realize the real reason why WWE wants to sign riddle, it really don't have nothing to do anything with his talent, it's the fact that WWE wants to continue to Cripple the Indies
